Arsenal target Kostas Manolas has been left out of Olympiacos' first league game of the season. 

The Gunners have been linked with a £6.5m move for the 23-year-old defender.

And speculation is set to intensify after Manolas was not included in the squad to face Niki Volou tonight. 

